<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= story.title %> - TravelTales</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body { font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <!-- Story Content -->
  <article class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Back Button -->
      <a href="/explore" class="inline-flex items-center text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-600 mb-8">
        <i class="bi bi-arrow-left mr-2"></i>
        Back to Stories
      </a>

      <!-- Story Header -->
      <header class="mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4"><%= story.title %></h1>
        <div class="flex items-center text-gray-600 mb-6">
          <i class="bi bi-calendar mr-2"></i>
          <span>Published on December 8, 2024</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Featured Image -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <img src="<%= story.image %>" alt="<%= story.title %>" class="w-full h-96 object-cover rounded-xl shadow-lg">
      </div>

      <!-- Story Content -->
      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6"><%= story.summary %></p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          This incredible journey began early in the morning as we set out to explore one of India's most magnificent destinations. The anticipation was palpable as we made our way through winding roads and breathtaking landscapes.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          What struck me most was the warmth of the local people and their eagerness to share stories about their homeland. Every conversation revealed new layers of history, culture, and tradition that made this trip truly unforgettable.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Journey Unfolds</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          As we ventured deeper into the heart of this beautiful region, each moment brought new discoveries. From ancient architecture to vibrant markets, from serene landscapes to bustling streets - every experience was a treasure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Memorable Moments</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Watching the sunrise over majestic landscapes</li>
          <li>Tasting authentic local delicacies</li>
          <li>Meeting fellow travelers from around the world</li>
          <li>Capturing stunning photographs at every turn</li>
          <li>Learning about local customs and traditions</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          This journey reminded me why I fell in love with travel in the first place. It's not just about the destinations we visit, but the people we meet, the stories we collect, and the memories we create along the way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Share Section -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Share this story</h3>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <a href="#" class="text-2xl text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition">
            <i class="bi bi-facebook"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="text-2xl text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-400 transition">
            <i class="bi bi-twitter"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="text-2xl text-gray-600 hover:text-pink-600 transition">
            <i class="bi bi-instagram"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <!-- Scripts -->
  <script src="/navbar.js"></script>
</body>
</html>